# key: rev
# --
Do a code review for all the changes.

Don't do any changes yourself, just surface the problems and rank them based on importance.

Make multiple passes.
Each pass should focus on a different type of issue in this order:
- logic errors;
- security;
- operation ordering;
- bad practices;
- magic strings and values;
- pattern improvements;
- reusability;
- maintainability;
- redundancy;